            <label><input type="radio" name="q1" value="no" required> No</label>
        </fieldset>

        <fieldset>
            <legend>2. The Shared Document Invite (Beginner)</legend>
            <p>Scenario: You get a notification from a cloud storage service (like Google Drive or Dropbox) saying a person you donâ€™t recognize,
